<FlowDocument xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml/presentation"
              ColumnWidth="400" FontSize="30" FontFamily="宋体"
              Foreground="Black">
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="36">定义：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="30">15倍速算法，15与某数相乘时，可先将某数扩大10倍后，再加上其10倍的折半积，即为其积。其口诀是：15乘先作10来算，然后再将半数添。可用公式</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="30">a×15=a×10+a÷2×10</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="30">进行速算。</Run>
        <LineBreak />
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="32">举例：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="28">36×15=</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="28" Foreground="Black">解答：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black"> 36×15</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=36×10+36÷2×10</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=360+180</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=540</Run>
    </Paragraph>
</FlowDocument>